<p style="text-align:justify"></p><p style="text-align:left">Dyrek&shy;tor Zespo&shy;&#322;u Szk&oacute;&#322; Tech&shy;nicz&shy;nych i Lice&shy;al&shy;nych w Pie&shy;cho&shy;wi&shy;cach infor&shy;mu&shy;je, &#380;e Komi&shy;tet Straj&shy;ko&shy;wy w ZSTiL w Pie&shy;cho&shy;wi&shy;cach pod&shy;j&#261;&#322; decy&shy;zj&#281; o zawie&shy;sze&shy;niu akcji straj&shy;ko&shy;wej z dniem <span class="numbers">18</span> kwiet&shy;nia <span class="numbers">2019</span> r. W zwi&#261;z&shy;ku z powy&#380;&shy;szym od dnia <span class="numbers">24</span>.<span class="numbers">04</span>.<span class="numbers">2019</span> r. odby&shy;wa&shy;&#322;y si&#281; b&#281;d&#261; w szko&shy;le zaj&#281;&shy;cia dydak&shy;tycz&shy;ne, wycho&shy;waw&shy;cze i opie&shy;ku&#324;&shy;cze wg pla&shy;nu.</p>
