<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://zsem.nazwa.pl/wordpress/?p=13421" rel="bookmark">Aceleague</a></h1>
<div class="entry-meta">
<span class="entry-date"><a href="http://zsem.nazwa.pl/wordpress/?p=13421" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2019-04-16T19:59:10+01:00">Kwiecie&#324; 16, 2019</time></a></span> <span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://zsem.nazwa.pl/wordpress/?author=2" rel="author">Marcin Spycha&#322;a</a></span></span>		</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
</header><!-- .entry-header --><div class="entry-content">
<p style="text-align: justify;">Nasza szkol&shy;na dru&shy;&#380;y&shy;na <span class="caps">CS</span>:<span class="caps">GO</span> (Aqu&shy;alis) zako&#324;&shy;czy&shy;&#322;a faz&#281; eli&shy;mi&shy;na&shy;cji Pol&shy;skiej Ligi Klas E-spor&shy;to&shy;wych Ace&shy;Le&shy;ague &mdash; sezon <span class="numbers">2018</span>/<span class="numbers">2019</span>. W tym roku mecze roz&shy;gry&shy;wa&shy;li&shy;&#347;my w naj&shy;wy&#380;&shy;szej kla&shy;sie (Cham&shy;pions). Infor&shy;mu&shy;je&shy;my, &#380;e na koniec sezo&shy;nu zasad&shy;ni&shy;cze&shy;go zaj&#281;&shy;li&shy;&#347;my <span class="numbers">3</span>-cie miej&shy;sce awan&shy;su&shy;j&#261;c na fina&shy;&#322;y <span class="caps">LAN</span>. Aktu&shy;al&shy;nie cze&shy;ka&shy;my na infor&shy;ma&shy;cj&#281; odno&shy;&#347;nie ter&shy;mi&shy;nu, miej&shy;sca i sys&shy;te&shy;mu roze&shy;gra&shy;nia fina&shy;&#322;&oacute;w. Gra&shy;tu&shy;la&shy;cje dla uczni&oacute;w !!</p>
<p>Osta&shy;tecz&shy;ne wyni&shy;ki: <a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1e3da5O7yZ0JUzlAoMi1zUseLLeTm3kkvPL2CUEssJ8o/edit?fbclid=IwAR1JQKMhg0da_BT4ob4fb4Ydf2QZD63v3X3UTBG6tNsL-7O-0W9sqGuG8aM#gid=430140417">tutaj</a>.</p>
</div><!-- .entry-content -->

