<div class="entry-meta">
<span class="entry-date"><a href="http://zsem.nazwa.pl/wordpress/?p=13365" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2019-04-08T07:57:20+01:00">Kwiecie&#324; 8, 2019</time></a></span> <span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://zsem.nazwa.pl/wordpress/?author=2" rel="author">Marcin Spycha&#322;a</a></span></span>		</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
</header><!-- .entry-header --><div class="entry-content">

<p style="text-align:justify">Dyrek&shy;tor ZSTiL w Pie&shy;cho&shy;wi&shy;cach infor&shy;mu&shy;je, &#380;e w zwi&#261;z&shy;ku z bra&shy;kiem poro&shy;zu&shy;mie&shy;nia Zwi&#261;z&shy;k&oacute;w Zawo&shy;do&shy;wych z Rz&#261;&shy;dem z dniem <span class="numbers">08</span>.<span class="numbers">04</span>.<span class="numbers">2019</span> r. w naszej szko&shy;le zawie&shy;szo&shy;ne zosta&shy;&#322;y zaj&#281;&shy;cia dydak&shy;tycz&shy;ne z powo&shy;du straj&shy;ku pra&shy;cow&shy;ni&shy;k&oacute;w szko&shy;&#322;y. </p>


<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="color: #ff0000;">Infor&shy;ma&shy;cja o odwo&shy;&#322;a&shy;niu straj&shy;ku zamiesz&shy;czo&shy;na zosta&shy;nie na stro&shy;nie inter&shy;ne&shy;to&shy;wej szko&shy;&#322;y oraz w dzien&shy;ni&shy;ku elek&shy;tro&shy;nicz&shy;nych w wia&shy;do&shy;mo&shy;&#347;ciach do rodzi&shy;c&oacute;w i uczni&oacute;w.</span></p>	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

