<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="http://zsem.nazwa.pl/wordpress/?p=13346" rel="bookmark"><span class="caps">DRODZY</span> <span class="caps">RODZICE</span></a></h1>
<div class="entry-meta">
<span class="entry-date"><a href="http://zsem.nazwa.pl/wordpress/?p=13346" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2019-04-07T07:29:38+01:00">Kwiecie&#324; 7, 2019</time></a></span> <span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://zsem.nazwa.pl/wordpress/?author=11" rel="author">Sylwia</a></span></span>		</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
</header><!-- .entry-header --><div class="entry-content">

<p style="text-align:justify;">
Dyrek&shy;tor Zespo&shy;&#322;u Szk&oacute;&#322; Tech&shy;nicz&shy;nych i Lice&shy;al&shy;nych w Pie&shy;cho&shy;wi&shy;cach infor&shy;mu&shy;je, &#380;e w prze&shy;pro&shy;wa&shy;dzo&shy;nym refe&shy;ren&shy;dum doty&shy;cz&#261;&shy;cym pod&shy;j&#281;&shy;cia akcji straj&shy;ko&shy;wej, kt&oacute;&shy;ra zapla&shy;no&shy;wa&shy;na jest od dnia <span class="numbers">08</span>.<span class="numbers">04</span>.<span class="numbers">2019</span>r. do odwo&shy;&#322;a&shy;nia, pra&shy;cow&shy;ni&shy;cy szko&shy;&#322;y opo&shy;wie&shy;dzie&shy;li si&#281; za pod&shy;j&#281;&shy;ciem straj&shy;ku na tere&shy;nie naszej szko&shy;&#322;y.
</p><p>
W zwi&#261;z&shy;ku z powy&#380;&shy;szym w przy&shy;pad&shy;ku bra&shy;ku poro&shy;zu&shy;mie&shy;nia Zwi&#261;z&shy;k&oacute;w Zawo&shy;do&shy;wych z Rz&#261;&shy;dem <span class="caps">RP</span> ist&shy;nie&shy;je praw&shy;do&shy;po&shy;do&shy;bie&#324;&shy;stwo, &#380;e z dniem <span class="numbers">08</span>.<span class="numbers">04</span>.<span class="numbers">2019</span>r. w szko&shy;le zawie&shy;szo&shy;ne zosta&shy;n&#261; zaj&#281;&shy;cia dydak&shy;tycz&shy;ne. Zwra&shy;cam si&#281; zatem z pro&#347;&shy;b&#261; o zapew&shy;nie&shy;nie swo&shy;im dzie&shy;ciom opie&shy;ki na czas straj&shy;ku pra&shy;cow&shy;ni&shy;k&oacute;w naszej pla&shy;c&oacute;w&shy;ki.
</p><p>
O pod&shy;j&#281;&shy;ciu straj&shy;ku czy te&#380; jego odwo&shy;&#322;a&shy;niu zosta&shy;n&#261; Pa&#324;&shy;stwo poin&shy;for&shy;mo&shy;wa&shy;ni nie&shy;zw&#322;ocz&shy;nie poprzez dzien&shy;nik elek&shy;tro&shy;nicz&shy;ny i stro&shy;n&#281; inter&shy;ne&shy;to&shy;w&#261; szko&shy;&#322;y.<br> Pro&shy;sz&#281; &#347;le&shy;dzi&#263; komu&shy;ni&shy;ka&shy;ty.</p>
<p>Z
powa&shy;&#380;a&shy;niem <br>Doro&shy;ta
Sob&shy;czy&#324;&shy;ska <br>Dyrek&shy;tor ZSTiL w
Pie&shy;cho&shy;wi&shy;cach
</p>
</div><!-- .entry-content -->

